dct_description_sm: "July 1992." Relief shown by contours, shading, and spot heights. "Israeli settlement names are not necessarily authoritative." UTM grid, Zone 36. Index of places and key to abbreviations on verso. "802077 (540876) 8-92." Shows armistice line of 1949, ceasefire line of 1967, and Jerusalem annexation line of 1980. Shows built-up areas, UNRWA refugee camps, and Israeli-developed areas (civilian and military) beyond 1949 armistice line. Roads, highways, tracks, railroads, shrines, ruins, and razed villages are shown. Gazetteer on verso. "Israeli settlement names are not necessarily authoritative. Boundary representation is not necessarily authoritative."
